template_3d_unit.comment: This component positions self over a unit in 3d space, shows the units name, zooms to on click, and sets a state when selected which refreshes whenever selection changes using the event system. Note that as we move to contexts 2.0 tagging the events is becoming less necessary as we can usually make this handle automatic in code, but still worth checking with coder to see if thats supported!
